{"type": "article", "id": 36227, "title": "推荐一个东京的包袋品牌，以及，这里有一些“法海”的杂志内图 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-12-30T02:48:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 330, "name": "可口可乐"}, {"id": 5247, "name": "羽绒服"}, {"id": 1576, "name": "欧莱雅"}, {"id": 26766, "name": "Sears"}, {"id": 36328, "name": "Frank Ocean"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 56, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161230104557FuRQrma6ATzM4bPG.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://fortune.com/2016/12/29/sears-holdings-ceo-retailer-loan/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国百货集团 Sears 的 CEO 开了 2 亿美元的信用证，股价大涨</b></a> | 周四，Sears 的股价大涨了 8.7%，至 8.89 美元每股。据 Bloomberg 所称，这是继 10 月 14 日之后最大的单日涨幅。在这次大涨之前，对比其竞争对手的表现，Sears 在今年的市值下降了约 60%。&nbsp;</p><p><b><a href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/us-loreal-digital-idUSKBN14G1IB\" rel=\"nofollow\">欧莱雅集团再次投资科技创业领域</a></b> | 欧莱雅集团于周二宣布，已投资了一支由私募基金 Partech Ventures 管理的一支针对互联网的早期投资基金，这也是欧莱雅在今年第二次投资科技创业领域。欧莱雅的首席数字运营官 Lubomira Rochet 在路透社的采访中表示，公司对新技术行业的投资将丰富品牌组合，强化供应链、研发和创新力量。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/shoes/nike-air-force-1-upstep-aluminum-obsidian/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike Air Force 1 推出了薰衣草紫色版本</a>，现已发售，售价为 138 美元。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102727SceC3rhiU7OWn8p5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102727vGyVm7c1nsuiwS94.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102728sxCIzZaWh823TSdm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102734sYuHXcE86jWpNBlV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>推荐一个来自东京的包袋品牌。<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/makavelic-spring-summer-2017-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">MAKAVELIC 于 2013 年创立</a>，以其街头风格迅速得到了关注，该品牌发布了它的 2017 春夏系列新品，都还挺好看的。来看看：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102748Q8iqB0rmUEzZOav4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612301027486dDFXR2CJYAU37nM.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102748TCXjKPF5G7Jiu1RA.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102749Ner6g0JR18tfVovC.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102749Kbiml9GaD4UpQePT.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102750sCPRad71A9uYJhe4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/descente-flagship-series-allterrain\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本运动休闲服装品牌 Descente，其主打的 Allterrain 系列羽绒服</a>还不错。其中，黑色的这件内层背心置有先进发热系统，提供 3 个温阶可随意调节。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102631rlLnAK1zOGuvbyj2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016123010265163EAyPcXMRlW7FhI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102652Qv76NfydsZktlOuL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102659ayVBHsX7cjQe1rJK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102704OW5AEtnqhDlMfHZg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>来双可口可乐的鞋子吧！近日，东京本地的球鞋品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/ubiq-x-coca-cola\" rel=\"nofollow\"> UBIQ，与可口可乐合作</a>，策划了联名鞋款。这次的联名款在复刻了 1940 年代可口可乐的经典 logo，共有三种颜色，包括 slip on 开口笑和高筒两个款式，就连鞋盒也是由可口可乐特别设计的。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102423jKJtz3kdYGy1DuES.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612301024369cn5RrjgfAdMQIwD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016123010243654V2tjliTzonRGXB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612301024429umSgfsjpPrvCb7h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612301024476k0qoWTMPu9Q5LGj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102453CkyQD4j7A0xSTq5e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102453LaeJbWIu1o4P5RQq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102454UAw2a3EqRolX0n6s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102500YA97KrzojyqpCfHd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/12/29/frank-ocean-boys-dont-cry-magazine/#slide-13\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hisnobiety 网站公开了一些《Boys Don’t Cry》的内页图</a>，这是美国知名 R&amp;B 歌手 Frank Ocean 在今年四月出的杂志，里面还有 Kanye West 和 A$AP 的内容。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102200X214PVdyADrn3vHa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612301022007xUTRlCqd0uQKWy4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102200PaWbYZMG4AEKjodT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102201khTPKSE4RF5yfDja.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102201te9HLBgX7jpf1UyC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102201jZxDfCMOitBbhpgV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230102207UGImFrP0nKalDEHx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161230104606sV0YgFqS9Q8xAaDj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/12/29/frank-ocean-boys-dont-cry-magazine/#slide-13\" rel=\"nofollow\">hisnobiety</a></p>"}